results.name: Logarithmic (or "LOG") transform of squares A000290.
link: Alois P. Heinz, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..435
formula: E.g.f.: exp(x)*(1 + 3*x + x^2)/(1 + exp(x)*x*(1 + x)). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Mar 06 2018
maple: logtr:= proc(p) local b; b:= proc(n) option remember; if n=0 then 1 else p(n)- add(k *binomial(n,k) *p(n-k) *b(k), k=1..n-1)/n fi end; n->b(n+1) end: a:= logtr(n-> n^2): seq(a(n), n=0..25); # _Alois P. Heinz_, Sep 14 2008
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
